text: Novomuraptalovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Muraptalovsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,289 as of 2010. There are 21 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Yermolayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Novomuraptalovo
